like I am for you

907
01:13:41,292 --> 01:13:45,129
and wishing that you're pining for me
like I do for you.

908
01:13:46,339 --> 01:13:47,882
Is this love?

909
01:14:04,357 --> 01:14:06,734
Or, on the other hand,

910
01:14:07,401 --> 01:14:09,820
