919
01:15:54,467 --> 01:15:56,093
I'd been looking everywhere for you.

920
01:15:57,094 --> 01:16:00,014
You only said you lived
around Cheongdam-dong, Gangnam-gu, Seoul.

921
01:16:00,806 --> 01:16:03,350
